{"tid":1250541,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞已與巴黎達成協議 1億+古天奴 交換尼馬","createTime":"2019-06-22T06:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:26:30.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"043abe9147cb7a5ed73c0f8e0083fee176bec429","tid":1250541,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:12:44.000Z","msg":"尼馬最新轉會消息兩則<br />\n<br />\n每日體育報：巴塞隆拿和巴黎聖日耳門正在透過中間人 Pini Zahavi 和 Kia Joorabchian 來達成尼馬的轉會協議，巴塞將會付出現金&euro;100M + 古天奴來完成轉會。<br />\n<br />\nDiario Sport報導：尼馬已同意巴塞提出的所有條件，包括降低個人薪酬，撤銷訴訟並公開表示他想要回歸魯營的希望。"},{"pid":"5eb3406e66d65654ec10d9b8ebef790cc4fc6816","tid":1250541,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"吓?"},{"pid":"c51ff129d2af2352b7c69ca3ce604bfc041dad31","tid":1250541,"uid":172507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae9a8dc01e1878039ca3004a17c6063ced4e04a","tid":1250541,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"正，一家便宜兩家著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f9e4a190746d27393535195cde44c330ee9686","tid":1250541,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"份報紙又鳩UP？"}]}